This paper deals with topic modeling, which is a subfield of information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also introduces a semi-supervised method for topic modeling, which involves optimization and convergence algorithms, making it relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper uses large, unstructured corpora of text documents, which is a common theme in data science (cs.DS).
